<p><b>Aleksandr Konstantinovich Petrov</b> (also <b>Alexander</b> or <b>Alexandre</b>) (<a href="/wiki/Russian_language" title="Russian language">Russian</a>: <span lang="ru" xml:lang="ru">Александр Константинович Петров</span>) (July 17, 1957) is a <a href="/wiki/Russia" title="Russia">Russian</a> <a href="/wiki/Animator" title="Animator">animator</a> and <a href="/wiki/Animation_director" title="Animation director">animation director</a>.</p>
